{
  "stem": "1249.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it's-- if three, four days, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I had a, a table a thing to, to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how I'm going to do it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to be with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wanted to be with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the decision was very hard, because I loved them just the same.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a wonderful human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was a wonderful human being.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said to myself, if I'm going to be with my grandfather, I won't be with my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was still a child, her child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he's going to be alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If I'm going to be with my mother, then he'll be alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If I'm going with my grandmother-- grandfather, then my mother is going to worry about me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I need her and my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it happened I had to go back to my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and if I would not, I'm sure I wouldn't be here today, because as I understood, when we were-- when-- somebody told me when they were taking to Auschwitz, the plane went-- plane-- the train went to Auschwitz, the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then my father died-- my grandfather died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was thrown out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somebody-- some, maybe 10 years ago, was here from Israel, same city where I came from.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she want to tell me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when she went this far, I said, I don't want to hear it, what happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to think back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't, because it's murder to look back what happened, innocent people, [SOBS] good people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For-- from the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They set us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
